<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2014-12-31</DATELINE><TITLE>Chapter 21 In Silico Models From Simple Networks to Complex Diseases</TITLE><BODY>Abstract In this chapter, we consider in silico modeling of diseases starting from some simple to some complex (and mathematical) concepts. Examples and applications of in silico modeling for some important categories of diseases (such as for cancers, infectious diseases, and neuronal diseases) are also given.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>